title: For the Future of the Cause: Why Would Anyone "Do" Youtube?
description:
Quite a few vegan activists (known to me) have already quit, amidst an increasingly hostile climate of (meaningless) infighting and slander.  There's only one reason for Henya to stay on youtube; she's already explained a hundred different reasons for her to go.
